After losing his family and becoming void of emotion but hatred, just wanted to kill the monsters he loathed.
I, Noh Eunha, regressed before my life ended in the deepest part of the Abyss Dungeon that was impossible for mankind to raid.
Since I’ve been reborn as a baby, let’s make this life different.
I will do anything for the sake of my happiness. I’ll kill in order to live, I’ll do my best to survive.
Even if I have to walk a thorny path by myself without anyone acknowledging me.
In this life, I will definitely—

Helmut was only a baby when he was left in the Forest of Pahe, an evil place full of beasts where sinners are banished for eternity. Luckily, one magical beast and an exiled swordsman take pity on him and raise him as their own. But with a dark seed growing inside him, Helmut decides to take up the sword to prevent the seed from turning him evil. As Helmut grows stronger, he seeks out the family that abandoned him, but will Helmut end up following his human heart or his beastly instincts?
(Source: Tapas)
